{"tid":1963707,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"其實點解經濟唔好 綜援户反而收入會增加?","createTime":"2020-04-08T10:24:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-08T12:59:10.000Z","uid":28159,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"77f1dbfe21334ac80bfb13a008df80983d6fad18","tid":1963707,"uid":28159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T10:24:50.000Z","msg":"你話長者津貼 傷殘津貼都算係幫輕下啲照顧佢哋嘅人嘅負擔<br />\n經濟唔好啲嘢平咗 錢好用咗<br />\n點解啲人收入下降嘅時候反而綜援會多咗收入?"},{"pid":"794f1e2a385f32301b14a2dc16b7ba8b42a5b475","tid":1963707,"uid":157799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T10:27:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2020年4月8日，係梓樂逝世5個月嘅日子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n今日有好多新聞，又有限聚令，大家可能忘記咗<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">每月8號</span>就係香港兒女周梓樂逝世嘅日子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家可唔可以幫一幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">這是香港人永久的痛</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PEc2uPw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPEc2uPw.png&h=44e78ee5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2019年11月4日晚上，科大生周梓樂從將軍澳尚德停車場墮樓，原因至今未明。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qydMWtg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqydMWtg.png&h=78033d4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6KOw7JO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6KOw7JO.png&h=85b332a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n梓樂墮樓後，黑警曾阻止救護車駛進，阻止人道救援。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3CaO9Rv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3CaO9Rv.jpg&h=d674bd89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而當晚，係有一位義士挺身而出，單人匹馬阻止黑警繼續發射催淚彈，同埋開路俾救護車駛入，結果被黑警打至頭破血流，並作出拘捕及起訴。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GttAP24.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGttAP24.jpg&h=8359b0c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n-<br />\n如果你記得周梓樂，請你都記得佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1786327/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1786327/page/1</a><br />\n-<br />\n2019年11月8日上午8時9分，據消息指，梓樂於伊利沙白醫院中，因心臟停頓而被宣告死亡。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wR5fPST.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwR5fPST.png&h=d91b3cd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而點解梓樂當晚會出現喺尚德停車場，好大可能係因為當晚有黑警結婚。當晚佢地為咗結婚擺酒，call哂成班綠衫狗過去、tg放題。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F3oX3dB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF3oX3dB.jpg&h=273e6a65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">徐岸暘 麥鈺熒</span></span><br />\n-<br />\n過去4個月之中，每個月嘅8號，都會有網民自發嘅悼念活動。而簡簡單單一個悼念儀式，政府、黑警竟然大費周章打壓，「梓樂之死並無可疑」的確相當有可疑。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a0VO9WV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa0VO9WV.png&h=b9e2527f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dcSt9WW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdcSt9WW.png&h=d643dc7b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bzegzoC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbzegzoC.png&h=c986eb69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n-<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">梓樂嘅死，我地必需時刻牢記，這是香港人與政權、黑警，不共戴天之仇。</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">仲有好多無名烈士，不明不白地死去了，就讓我們在這天一同紀念。</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PZVjxhK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPZVjxhK.png&h=2b122f37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">港共政權藉疫情為由，推出限聚令，打壓為實，致今天我們難以進行公眾拜祭活動。是故今晚會有網上悼念活動，亦請大家於<span style=\"color: red;\">8時9分</span>自行默哀1分鐘。</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UXCYNS2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUXCYNS2.png&h=9048652b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但願各位手足不要氣餒，革命往往是要花很長的時間才能達成，而且身邊同行者未必多。想當初國父孫中山搞革命之年，乃封建滿清之時，愚民豈不是更多，同行者不是更難找到。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">君子報仇，十年未晚</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">今日未報，時辰未到</span><br />\n<br />\n我地即管同呢個政權鬥長命，最緊要要保全自己嘅性命。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jdkzk9s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjdkzk9s.png&h=748484b0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fbiX3nO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfbiX3nO.png&h=a2cdcef8&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"93751055c9e0284f78d66fd2d351187af664a784","tid":1963707,"uid":118647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T10:27:19.000Z","msg":"呢班新移民、底層係政府支持既基本盤黎，點可以唔對佢地好啲呢"},{"pid":"09ef48dd902f0aaab27918b6edfe67eb17a851a3","tid":1963707,"uid":28159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"93751055c9e0284f78d66fd2d351187af664a784","tid":1963707,"uid":118647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T10:27:19.000Z","msg":"呢班新移民、底層係政府支持既基本盤黎，點可以唔對佢地好啲呢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T12:59:10.000Z","msg":"最大問題係冇咩人去question"}]}